Package org.pepstock.charba.client.configuration

Interface HasMinMaxCallbacksHandler<T>

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IsLinearAxis, IsNumericAxis
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CartesianCategoryAxis, CartesianLinearAxis, CartesianLogarithmicAxis, CartesianTimeAxis, CartesianTimeSeriesAxis, ColorAxis, ColorLogarithmicAxis, RadialAxis, SizeAxis, SizeLogarithmicAxis
    interface HasMinMaxCallbacksHandler<T>
    Interface which is implemented for the axes class to manage min, max, suggestedMin and suggestedMax callbacks.
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero

    • Method Summary
